---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Gnome Sequencing">
  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> / <a href="/applications/">Applications</a> / Gnome Sequencing</div>
      <h1>Gnome Sequencing</h1>
      <p>High-throughput short- and long-read sequencing for gnome-scale projects.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <section>
    <div class="container" style="max-width:760px;">
      <div class="cards mb-2">
        <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">⚡</div><h3>Short-read WGS</h3><p>Whole-gnome sequencing at up to 30× coverage using GnomeSeq X Plus.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">🔬</div><h3>Long-read WGS</h3><p>Ultra-long reads for resolving complex gnome repeats via GnomePore P2.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">🎯</div><h3>Targeted Gnome</h3><p>Capture-based enrichment for gene panels and specific gnome loci.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">🍄</div><h3>Metagnomics</h3><p>Community profiling of complex gnome-associated microbial ecosystems.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="alert alert-info">
        Ready to start a gnome sequencing project? <a href="/platform/">Access the platform →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
